body_html:
Im using Macbook Pro to build the quantized model. The version of tensorflow is 1.2 in my mac.
Im trying to deploy the quantized model in windows. The version of tensorflow is 1.2 in my windows.

I compiled it using bazel.

This is how is generated it,

  bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/transform_graph \
--in_graph=tmp/stripped.pb \
--out_graph=tmp/quantized_gender.pb \
--inputs='Mul' \
--outputs='final_result' \
--transforms='
  strip_unused_nodes(type=float, shape="1,299,299,3")
  fold_constants(ignore_errors=true)
  fold_batch_norms
  fold_old_batch_norms
  quantize_weights'

body:
Im using Macbook Pro to build the quantized model. The version of tensorflow is 1.2 in my mac.
Im trying to deploy the quantized model in windows. The version of tensorflow is 1.2 in my windows. 

I compiled it using bazel.


This is how is generated it,

```
  bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/transform_graph \
--in_graph=tmp/stripped.pb \
--out_graph=tmp/quantized_gender.pb \
--inputs='Mul' \
--outputs='final_result' \
--transforms='
  strip_unused_nodes(type=float, shape="1,299,299,3")
  fold_constants(ignore_errors=true)
  fold_batch_norms
  fold_old_batch_norms
  quantize_weights'
```
